data.description: 2.48 acres on 12 acre pond with 210' of waterfront. 965 sq. ft. workshop with electricity, (wired for 220) water, a bay door and parking pad for RV. Beautiful in-ground pool with three gently flowing waterfalls. Stunning view from 23'x12' back deck or 16'x12' sun room. The interior has heavy warm rich naturally stained molding. Entry & family room have hardwood floors. 2 fireplaces, one in the family room & one in the downstairs rec room. Spacious dining room. Granite counters in the kitchen along with a breakfast bar and abundant cabinets. Owner's bedroom on main floor, with huge walk-in closet and bath with separate shower and separate garden tub . It even has a room to store holiday decorations. Downstairs is another huge family living space with the 2nd fireplace, office or computer room and three bedrooms and two baths all open to the backyard. Great storage. New roof 5 years ago & new water heater 2 years ago. It's definitely great value!! Convenient to I-20 and shopping
